{"id":97584,"type":1,"name":"手塚治虫漫画全集 三つ目がとおる","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/5d/5e/97584_gLMvp.jpg","rating":{"total":5,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":0,"6":0,"7":1,"8":3,"9":0,"10":0},"score":7},"summary":"著名日本漫画家手冢治虫的大作，从1974年到1978年3月在《周刊少年Magazine》连载。故事围绕古代文明、民俗传说以及各种未解之谜展开，传奇色彩浓郁。剧情明快活泼，与作者《周刊少年CHAMPION》同期连载的《BLACK JACK》（怪医秦博士）沉重阴郁的基调形成了鲜明对比。亦正亦邪的主人公极具魅力，一开始是每月刊载，后来改成每周刊载一回，1977年获第1届讲谈社漫画赏。日本电视台于1985年推出动画特别篇《三眼神童-恶魔岛的王子》，之后东京电视台于1990年TV动画化。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>三眼小子</li><li><span>册数: </span>13</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/1318\">手塚治虫</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/128\">講談社</a>、<a href=\"/person/8365\">時報文化</a>、<a href=\"/person/8050\">文化傳信</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/6704\">週刊少年マガジン</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>三眼神童</li><li><span>开始: </span>1974年</li><li><span>结束: </span>1978年</li>","collection":{"wish":2,"collect":6,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"手塚治虫","count":2},{"name":"搜索用","count":1},{"name":"童年","count":1},{"name":"漫画","count":1}],"crt":[{"id":26713,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d2/c1/26713_crt_BdADw.jpg","name":"胡子老爹","desc":"配角"},{"id":27123,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/32/2f/27123_crt_2z1AV.jpg","name":"莫亚","desc":"配角"}],"staff":[{"id":1318,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/76/cf/1318_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"手冢治虫","desc":"作者"},{"id":128,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2f/b1/128_prsn_nHh14.jpg","name":"讲谈社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8365,"image":"","name":"台湾时报文化","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8050,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/af/d7/8050_prsn_VkR3u.jpg","name":"文化传信集团有限公司","desc":"出版社"},{"id":6704,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a4/61/6704_prsn_rEcx7.jpg","name":"周刊少年Magazine","desc":"连载杂志"}],"relations":[{"id":6605,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b7/f9/6605_mNdD1.jpg","title":"三つ目がとおる","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/6605"},{"id":86984,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/75/6d/86984_leEID.jpg","title":"三つ目がとおる","type":"不同版本","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/86984"}],"comic":[{